          good   explanation  for  the  large  deflection  angle  of  the
          northeastern  outflow.  Other  H2  emission features around the
          IRAS  4  region  are  discussed briefly. Some of them are newly
          found  outflows,  and some are associated with outflows already
          known before.


   
