          the first such system to be discovered outside the Local Group.
          Based  on  a  sequence of 25 Chandra observations that sample a
          wide  range of orbital phases, we find a period of 32.688 $\pm$
          0.002  hours,  which  we  interpret  as  an orbital period. The
